title: Interactive html quizzes for students of GRE/GMAT/science/Langua
description:
Interactive Quizzes for college students studying for GRE, GMAT (words list),
languages, science, chemistry, physics, astronomy, mathematics,
and Kinyarwanda (language of Rwanda, Africa).

Each html file is standalone and needs evalquiz.js to evaluate
the quiz. 

See the file list for topics of your interest.

About 60,000 questions in form of static html pages, tested
the quizzes in Chrome 2013/Firefox 4/IE 6.
